Package: recmap
Type: Package
Title: Compute The Rectangular Statistical Cartogram
Version: 0.1.2
Author: Christian Panse
Maintainer: Christian Panse <Christian.Panse@gmail.com>
Description: The 'recmap' package provides an interface and a C++ implementation of the 
  RecMap MP2 construction heuristic (see 'citation("recmap")' for details).
  Documentation about 'recmap' is provided by a vignette included in this package.
License: GPL-3
LazyData: TRUE
Depends: R (>= 3.2), Rcpp (>= 0.12.4)
SystemRequirements: C++11
Suggests: knitr, testthat 
LinkingTo: Rcpp (>= 0.12.4)
VignetteBuilder: knitr
NeedsCompilation: yes
URL: http://cartodraw.science/recmap/
